# Data report overview
The dataset examined has the following dimensions:


---------------------------------
Feature                    Result
------------------------ --------
Number of observations        180

Number of variables            68
---------------------------------

The features for this database come from the [UCI HAR Dataset](http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Human+Activity+Recognition+Using+Smartphones).
Except for `activity` and `subject` each variable in this dataset measures the average of all values of  corresponding variable with the same name in the UCI HAR Dataset for a specific activity and subject.
